    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你也明白，如果要去解释一个想法，这个想法就从根本上改变了。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/991298d1a85584d52f9ce74285d29c9f.poster.avif?t=1770042877\" width=780 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/991298d1a85584d52f9ce74285d29c9f.webm?t=1770042877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/991298d1a85584d52f9ce74285d29c9f.mp4?t=1770042877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《UNBEATABLE》是一款充满日式动画气息的节奏冒险游戏。在这里，你将在舞台上大杀四方，同时真的把舞台砸个稀烂。在节奏玩法中，你只需要两个按键，一个管上，一个管下 – 超级好懂！而复杂的地方就在于真正做到。不要翻车喔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的一半内容是四处游走，自顾自玩。另一半则需要追上他人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/a7c6f32ec6bdf9e2be2a3224b9f94ed8.poster.avif?t=1770042877\" width=780 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/a7c6f32ec6bdf9e2be2a3224b9f94ed8.webm?t=1770042877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/a7c6f32ec6bdf9e2be2a3224b9f94ed8.mp4?t=1770042877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有个粉红色头发的女孩，名叫 节拍 – 也就是你。你有许多事情要操心：警察到处都是，而且还都不明不白就生你的气。不过你也真是的，非要去结交那些明明白白招警察恨的家伙们。不过我懂什么啦？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/91277bea999c9063aeaf5ce837c84ebc.poster.avif?t=1770042877\" width=780 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/91277bea999c9063aeaf5ce837c84ebc.webm?t=1770042877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/91277bea999c9063aeaf5ce837c84ebc.mp4?t=1770042877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去和人们交谈，帮助他们（或者不帮也行，我又不是你老妈！），大办演唱会，还有狠揍警察条子 – 然后逃走。还有怪物之类的玩意。真不知道这里是怎么了？！？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切都在巨大的布景中演化到极限，一切都岌岌可危。是音乐将你带到这里，也会是音乐引领你度过难关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*如果是 1999 年，这部分就会被称为：“言出必行，摇滚到底”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/49245a091cf446df1b4ea8fb24d6aba0.poster.avif?t=1770042877\" width=780 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/49245a091cf446df1b4ea8fb24d6aba0.webm?t=1770042877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240620/extras/49245a091cf446df1b4ea8fb24d6aba0.mp4?t=1770042877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《UNBEATABLE》的完全街机模式自成一体，有自己的进度体系和完整的在线组成部分。内容包括修改器、大量歌曲（后续还会追加更多！）以及等待征服的挑战板 – 要做的事情，从普通的“简单模式通关一首歌曲”到复杂的“在滑板上解开远古谜题”，林林总总，不一而足。刚刚说的只是假设而已。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>**如果是 1999 年，这部分就会被称为：“活在当下，尽情派对”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特性：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事模式：6–8小时 街机模式：<i>无限</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讨厌你的各色角色！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兴许还有不讨厌你的家伙！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >街机模式有可爱的小头像供玩家定制，还可解锁物品 - 我觉得这挺赞的</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美画面！虽然是想大说特说，但画面这玩意一目了然啦</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一整部双碟专辑，原曲绝赞</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >再加上这些歌曲的不插电版本</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>啊，混音版也没落下</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些歌曲统统可以通过游玩剧情版或单纯游玩街机版解锁！不喜欢看剧情的人有福了</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内容会让你在现实里心有所感！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这就是日式动画</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想想看吧，QTE 就是没有音乐的节奏游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拜托，不管怎样，游戏标题要么就全部大写，要么就全部小写。帮帮忙吧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而那个想法回过头来会改变你自己。</p></li></ul>",
